{"tid":594963,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★或因美國制裁，伊朗已無法使用蘋果App Store","createTime":"2018-03-16T09:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T00:41:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0d01266ebf0564d65341b2a6996326cf829a6a","tid":594963,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:31:54.000Z","msg":"2018-3-16 9:01:42<br />\n<br />\n3月16日消息 根據Bleeping Computer的報導，伊朗的iPhone用戶今天已不能訪問App Store，看起來似乎是整個國家已被遮罩。雖然蘋果並不在伊朗銷售手機或經營App Store，但伊朗人仍然可以從別的國家進口蘋果產品，並訪問App Store中適用於其他地區的部分產品。現在看來，蘋果已經封鎖了這個漏洞，阻止來自伊朗境內的任何流量以任何身份進入App Store<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前尚不清楚推動這一變化的原因是什麼，但<span style=\"color: red;\">應該跟美國總統特朗普去年對伊朗的制裁有關</span>。蘋果沒有對這些變化做出聲明，也沒有立即返回評論請求。如果禁令是永久性的，那麼伊朗iOS設備的擁有者將不得不通過VPN來使用App Store，使其顯示位置變為另一個國家，顯然，這將使得使用Apple設備變得更加困難。<br />\n<br />\n試圖訪問伊朗App Store的用戶現在會收到一條消息：&ldquo;App Store在您所在的國家或地區無法使用&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/html/iphone/351336.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2Fhtml%2Fiphone%2F351336.htm&d=uvnUwBOD0%2FcZEeC6XjBEZBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6eb48f70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/html/iphone/351336.htm</a>"},{"pid":"64f88a3ba8bba33cc41439913a462efb45608674","tid":594963,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fb232c53b3e04477c9693033bfceed2f875928","tid":594963,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:53:39.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭撚用咩現代科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f816621007c0a4ddf213f066870bbff33d02f791","tid":594963,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T22:59:04.000Z","msg":"用an 機lor"},{"pid":"b0dd9d23b8acedfb34109178b80c7b4d7543be19","tid":594963,"uid":82587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f816621007c0a4ddf213f066870bbff33d02f791","tid":594963,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T22:59:04.000Z","msg":"用an 機lor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T23:39:59.000Z","msg":"好似google play 一直ban 左呢個置家"},{"pid":"0207c973d588bcd040e8303578c6349f20547e8f","tid":594963,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T00:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用an 機lor</blockquote>好似google play 一直ban 左呢個置家</blockquote><br />\nwindows phone或成最大贏家"}]}